</div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-12"><p><span style="color: #ffffff;">In <em>Sniper Rust VR’s</em> single-player campaign, you play as a highly-skilled hired gun, employed by a covert agency, called upon to put your sniping skills to the test.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">You’re pitted against an armed militia global uprising in this 18-level, heart-pounding globe-trotting adventure that is guaranteed to deliver plenty of thrills and excitement.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">As you navigate your way through four diverse, photorealistic environments, face off against unique enemy AI including undercover snipers, air assaults and other hidden traps! Keep your eyes on the prize and your aim steady!</span></p>
